### Description
Runs when a plugin is first installed into the EmDash CMS.

### Method
N/A (Hook)

### Endpoint
N/A (Hook)

### Parameters
#### Event
- **pluginId** (string) - Required - The unique identifier of the plugin being installed.

### Request Example
```javascript
{
  "pluginId": "my-custom-plugin"
}
```

### Response
#### Success Response
No return value expected.

#### Response Example
N/A
```

```APIDOC
## plugin:activate

### Description
Runs when a plugin is enabled or activated.

### Method
N/A (Hook)

### Endpoint
N/A (Hook)

### Parameters
#### Event
- **pluginId** (string) - Required - The unique identifier of the plugin being activated.

### Request Example
```javascript
{
  "pluginId": "my-custom-plugin"
}
```

### Response
#### Success Response
No return value expected.

#### Response Example
N/A
```

```APIDOC
## plugin:deactivate

### Description
Runs when a plugin is disabled or deactivated.

### Method
N/A (Hook)

### Endpoint
N/A (Hook)

### Parameters
#### Event
- **pluginId** (string) - Required - The unique identifier of the plugin being deactivated.

### Request Example
```javascript
{
  "pluginId": "my-custom-plugin"
}
```

### Response
#### Success Response
No return value expected.

#### Response Example
N/A
```

```APIDOC
