### Installing Plugins > From the Marketplace > Browse and Install

Source: https://docs.emdashcms.com/plugins/installing

To install a marketplace plugin, navigate to Plugins > Marketplace in the admin panel, select a plugin, review its details and capability consent dialog, and click Install. The plugin is downloaded, stored in your site’s R2 bucket, and loaded into the sandbox runner, becoming active immediately.

