Source: https://docs.emdashcms.com/plugins/api-routes

A practical example demonstrating how to define API routes within a plugin using Zod for input validation.

```APIDOC
## Example Plugin with API Routes

This example shows a plugin defining two API routes: `status` and `submissions`.

```javascript
import { definePlugin } from "emdash";
import { z } from "astro/zod";


export default definePlugin({
  id: "forms",
  version: "1.0.0",


  storage: {
    submissions: {
      indexes: ["formId", "status", "createdAt"],
    },
  },


  routes: {
    // Simple route
